\" /> <br />\n多幾個功能都睇到眼殘，一係縮到黃豆咁大粒<br />\n所以就算移植過去嘅game，遊戲體驗上點都同原平台差啲<br />\n賣點得返可以出街玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔通我係屋企玩都貪佢夠lag又可以睇壞眼咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係好創新嘅idea，冇乜留意新game，我淨係諗到Ingress<br />\n著眼玩家互動，彌補遊戲性<br />\n<br />\n終歸都係手機呢個平台先天不足，二奶命<br />\nPC/主機做到嘅，手機未必得<br />\n手機做到嘅，PC/主機多數得，仲要做得更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a21ebfeb4d1b838f0572ef1ed0c3704c1e1b0f1","tid":778784,"uid":48109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f053891eb4d6ffc0caf7e6fa10db6b1299dd1ad9","tid":778784,"uid":59952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e02e9400cf66cad51a8e6590014f0c053b8cbbf","tid":778784,"uid":48109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:18:28.000Z","msg":"日系韓系多數都係呢類抽卡GAME自動打，<br />\n不如試下 Brawl Stars  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:16:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上哂癮<br />\n有fd 一齊開住discord 仲撚爽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:51:17.000Z","msg":"識野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa71565fe0e8780aeab4de5ce0d2c473c258142","tid":778784,"uid":193514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:32:32.000Z","msg":"手機做到好似NDS咁實多人玩架<br />\n你試下做番好似POKEMON點會無人玩 <br />\n但無人會做D唔賺錢既野<br />\n梗係做D要人課金既GAME架啦"},{"pid":"b4f4ff82415e7895c503efdf4da61d111bd8973d","tid":778784,"uid":193514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fa71565fe0e8780aeab4de5ce0d2c473c258142","tid":778784,"uid":193514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:32:32.000Z","msg":"手機做到好似NDS咁實多人玩架<br />\n你試下做番好似POKEMON點會無人玩 <br />\n但無人會做D唔賺錢既野<br />\n梗係做D要人課金既GAME架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:35:05.000Z","msg":"同堆手機GAME既對象多數唔係細路<br />\n無得AUTO既GAME 邊個得閒玩<br />\n有時間都直接去玩CONSOLE GAME啦"},{"